---
import Card from "@components/base/Card.astro";
---

<div id="about"
  class="w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted-100 dark:bg-muted-1000"
>
  <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <div class="col-span-12 ltablet:col-span-4 lg:col-span-4">
      <div
        class="h-full ptablet:max-w-lg ptablet:mx-auto flex items-center mb-8 ltablet:mb-0 lg:mb-0"
      >
        <div
          class="text-center ltablet:text-left lg:text-left font-sans space-y-4"
        >
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4">
            <h2
              class="col-start-2 col-span-11 font-sans text-2xl text-center font-medium ptablet:text-2xl lg:text-2xl mb-4 text-muted-800 dark:text-amber-600"
            >
              Кто мы?
            </h2>

            <p
              class="col-start-2 col-span-11 text-lg ptablet:text-lg lg:text-lg text-muted-500 dark:text-muted-400 text-sm ptablet:text-sm lg:text-sm"
            >
              Мы студенты Финансового университета при Правительстве РФ
            </p>

            <div
              x-cloak
              class="relative overflow-hidden col-start-2 col-span-11"
              x-intersect="activeStep = ''"
            >
              <div class="swiper-container" x-ref="container">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                  <!-- Slides -->
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <Card class="'p-6'">
                      <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-8 font-sans">
                        <i
                          class="iconify w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-amber-700"
                          data-icon="fa6-solid:quote-left"></i>
                        <p class="text-muted-500 dark:text-muted-300">
                          Всем привет! Я Даша.
                        </p>
                        <div class="w-full flex items-center gap-3">
                          <div class="shrink-0 inline-flex relative w-10 h-10">
                            <img
                              src="../../../public/img/illustrations/persons/dasha.jpg"
                              class="object-cover max-w-full rounded-full dark:border-transparent shadow-sm"
                              alt="User image"
                            />
                          </div>
                          <div>
                            <h4
                              class="font-medium text-sm text-muted-800 dark:text-muted-100"
                            >
                              Дарья Агапенкова
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-muted-400">Machine Leaner</p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </Card>
                  </div>
                  <!-- Slides -->
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <Card class="'p-6'">
                      <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-8 font-sans">
                        <i
                          class="iconify w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-amber-700"
                          data-icon="fa6-solid:quote-left"></i>
                        <p class="text-muted-500 dark:text-muted-300">
                          Всем привет! Я Наташа.
                        </p>
                        <div class="w-full flex items-center gap-3">
                          <div class="shrink-0 inline-flex relative w-10 h-10">
                            <img
                              src="../../../public/img/illustrations/persons/natashka.jpg"
                              class="object-cover max-w-full rounded-full dark:border-transparent shadow-sm"
                              alt="User image"
                            />
                          </div>
                          <div>
                            <h4
                              class="font-medium text-sm text-muted-800 dark:text-muted-100"
                            >
                              Данилкина Наталья
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-muted-400">
                              Backend developer
                            </p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </Card>
                  </div>
                  <!-- Slides -->
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <Card class="'p-6'">
                      <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-8 font-sans">
                        <i
                          class="iconify w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-amber-700"
                          data-icon="fa6-solid:quote-left"></i>
                        <p class="text-muted-500 dark:text-muted-300">
                          Всем привет! Я Лиза
                        </p>
                        <div class="w-full flex items-center gap-3">
                          <div class="shrink-0 inline-flex relative w-10 h-10">
                            <img
                              src="../../../public/img/illustrations/persons/liza.jpg"
                              class="object-cover max-w-full rounded-full dark:border-transparent shadow-sm"
                              alt="User image"
                            />
                          </div>
                          <div>
                            <h4
                              class="font-medium text-sm text-muted-800 dark:text-muted-100"
                            >
                              Вайсберг Елизавета
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-muted-400">
                              Frontend developer
                            </p>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </Card>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div x-data="swiper()" class="carousel-container">
                <div
                  class="carousel-controls flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
                >
                  <button
                    class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-muted-600 hover:text-primary-600 dark:text-muted-300 dark:hover:text-muted-100 hover:bg-muted-200 dark:hover:bg-muted-900 transition-colors duration-300"
                    @click="swiper.slidePrev()"
                  >
                    <i class="iconify" data-icon="lucide:arrow-left"></i>
                  </button>

                  <button
                    class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-muted-600 hover:text-primary-600 dark:text-muted-300 dark:hover:text-muted-100 hover:bg-muted-200 dark:hover:bg-muted-900 transition-colors duration-300"
                    @click="swiper.slideNext()"
                  >
                    <i class="iconify" data-icon="lucide:arrow-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-12 ltablet:col-span-4 lg:col-span-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12">
        <h2
          class="col-start-2 col-span-11 font-sans text-2xl text-center font-medium ptablet:text-2xl lg:text-2xl mb-4 text-muted-800 dark:text-amber-600"
        >
          Что это?
        </h2>

        <p
          class="col-start-2 col-span-11 text-lg ptablet:text-lg lg:text-lg text-muted-500 dark:text-muted-400 text-sm ptablet:text-sm lg:text-sm"
        >
          ДЕН Ь - проект команды молодых разработчиков, созданный для генерации
          изображений в выбранной стилизации
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-12 ltablet:col-span-4 lg:col-span-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12">
        <h2
          class="col-start-2 col-span-11 font-sans text-2xl text-center font-medium ptablet:text-2xl lg:text-2xl mb-4 text-muted-800 dark:text-amber-600"
        >
          Как с нами связаться?
        </h2>

        <p
          class="col-start-2 col-span-11 text-lg ptablet:text-lg lg:text-lg text-muted-500 dark:text-muted-400 text-sm ptablet:text-sm lg:text-sm"
        >
          Если у вас есть вопросы, можете связаться с нами в телегамме. Также
          ждем вас на нашей страничке github
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
